description.full: This game was classified by the community with the following category scores - Violence=0/3, Sex=0/3, Mature Content=0/3. Do you love famous celebrities? Do you know your celebs from all walks of life, from all over the world, from the entertainment industry to science to politics—and cartoon characters and those that lived in past centuries? Name it and we have it! Prove just how amazing you and your avatar are, go against your friends with hundreds of questions across 5 challenging levels!
